      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 25,
      "message": "Hello Jim,\n\nTo be able to change the sate of the Control Loop the rest endpoint accepts a list of Control Loop name and version, and not the definition name and version, but when I retrieve the ToscaConceptIdentifier it will bring the definition name and version and it will not affect the state change.\n\nI had two options to address this, this way or I had to change the original rest endpoint where it accepts a put method and change the state by the ToscaConceptIdentifier.",
